Text.Value: They said you've done this before. Well, I've got one fireteam to spare and whatever supplies you need, but I... I can't risk them taking over any more of my men.

Responses.ScriptNotes: You're tired, exhausted and scared after engaging in some of the hardest fighting of your life.

Text.Value: Put that last Morph down and do it fast. We... we'll hold as best we can.
